# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased] 2018-12-05
### Changed

- Added changelog
- Turned arrays into vectors
- Fixed memory leaks related to the conversion

## [Unreleased] 2018-12-03
### Changed

- Turned the vector product to scalar product in the energy equation
- Fixed the calculation of the conservation law
- Timestep set to the minimum between the min value calculated for each particle and the previous value + 10%
- Reset the number of neighbors to 0 before each findNeighbors
- fixed the calculation of the energy in the update phase (wrong dt used)
- discovered an issue in the Octree that we were using, that caused the momentum to be wrong

